#: includes/class-settings.php:634
msgid "Intro duck-in second"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:641 includes/class-settings.php:697
msgid "seconds"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:642
msgid ""
"The intro plays at 100% until this second. From here it starts fading down "
"and the podcast voice fades in."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:647
msgid "Intro volume under podcast"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:655
msgid ""
"Volume to which the intro fades during duck-in, before reaching 0. Example: "
"30 = intro fades to 30% while the voice comes in."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:660
msgid "Second at which intro reaches 0"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:668
msgid "seconds (empty = until the end of the intro file)"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:669
msgid ""
"Exact second at which the intro reaches silence. If left empty, the fade "
"lasts until the end of the intro file."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:674
msgid "Knee: seconds to reach duck volume"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:682
msgid "seconds after duck start (empty = linear)"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:684
msgid ""
"Seconds after the duck start at which the intro has already dropped to the "
"duck volume %. A short value (e.g. 1) gives a sharp initial drop followed by "
"a long gentle tail. The outro uses the exact mirror curve automatically. "
"Leave empty for a linear fade."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:690
msgid "Seconds before end for outro fade-in"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:698
msgid ""
"The outro starts playing in the background this many seconds before the "
"podcast voice ends. When the voice ends, it rises to 100%."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:703
msgid "Outro volume under podcast"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-settings.php:711
msgid ""
"Maximum volume of the outro while the podcast voice is still playing. When "
"the voice ends, the outro rises to 100%."
msgstr ""

